    agus.gunit
    The main guidance unit package containing the basic classes for use in the program
    agus.gunit.execution
    Contains all different executions that guide the vessel to the desired location
    agus.gunit.execution.assist
    Contains different assists to be used by an execution
    agus.gunit.vessel
    This package contains the objects needed to get all information of the vessel and the automatic staging
    agus.gunit.vessel.stage
    This package contains the objects needed to get all information of the vessel
    agus.ui
    This packages usage is to hold all the different ui, or display configurations
